The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for detecting barcodes, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models for this task suggests that it may also fall under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of real-time processing, which suggests that it may fall under the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR) or data structures (cs.DS) for efficient processing.
